title: ‘Succession’ S3, E6 Precap
description:
Chris and Wos react to a packed and tense Season 3, Episode 5 of ‘Succession,’ before making some predictions and wish lists about what’s to come in Episode 6 and beyond.

Hosts: Chris Ryan and Wosny Lambre
Producer: Bobby Wagner
